A vast intricate mechanical clockwork mechanism viewed from above, with dozens of interconnected bronze and copper gears of varying sizes meshing together in perfect harmony, some gears featuring miniature architectural elements like domed temples and modern office buildings integrated into their teeth, steam wisps rising from the connections, the whole assembly floating above a misty Indian landscape at golden hour, rich warm sepia and amber tones with hints of verdigris patina, vintage technical illustration style with cross-hatching and fine linework details
